fetcher before a classifier in metaflow is not possible. Currently to do this, you’ll have to use the Apply Classifier step

@Ted

That’s a decision on the infra side whether to support opencv as something accessible in UDFs.

I believe the answer is yes for Apply UDF but no for Fetchers (because Fetchers run in webdriver-tasks)

@shaunak @Ashish @Karthik S — on making a call whether to support opencv as a library, which would require having all of our app-tasks and webdriver-tasks workers support opencv in perpetuity
